translations: v．补充，重新填满：将某物恢复到原来的水平或数量。
· She replenishes the food supplies every week.
她每周都会补充食物供应。

phrs.translation: 干性皮肤补充, 微量元素皮肤干燥, 补充皮肤干燥

sentences.sentence: This replenishes the seed content of the desert soil.
sentences.translation: 这使得种子在沙漠泥土中播撒。

sentences.sentence: The skin of your scalp replenishes every month .
sentences.translation: 皮肤你的头皮补充每个月都有。

sentences.sentence: While each shipment replenishes items that sell well, each also includes new items.
sentences.translation: 每次运货都会去补足那些畅销品同时也会上新品。
